14
00:00:51.410 --> 00:00:54.810
So the few things to remember
about linear gradients is

15
00:00:54.810 --> 00:00:56.820
if you're using a key term
don't forget the word to.

16
00:00:58.850 --> 00:01:03.200
And the top, when you're talking
about degrees, the top is zero and

17
00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:04.680
the angles go clockwise.

18
00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:08.200
