it wasn't necessary back then.

23
00:01:24.240 --> 00:01:28.630
And then the angles actually
went counterclockwise.

24
00:01:28.630 --> 00:01:31.430
So generally it doesn't make that
much of a difference because

25
00:01:31.430 --> 00:01:33.090
gradients usually just go top to bottom.

26
